\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2031ed573281042d2cfd55927abe3318f48844f","tid":1663453,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"783d90e15c420497d5a7a6ed670270243b53e750","tid":1663453,"uid":198320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T11:57:23.000Z","msg":"自從中五就有 因為一件事<br />\n無睇過醫生<br />\n會因為一件事不斷loop 個腦會不停自己係咁問自己<br />\n可以係好小既事 都可以自我放到好大<br />\n又細到大都靠自己克制<br />\n其實好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:57:18.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=e4d23a9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"f8671e7e2055a19de2c84bc26be6a02edb7a905b","tid":1663453,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T22:51:39.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=ca610453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=4582c709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a><br />\n戒J 前後對比圖<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.noj1314.258club.com/forumdisplay.php?fid=63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.noj1314.258club.com%2Fforumdisplay.php%3Ffid%3D63&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=cd43cd78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.noj1314.258club.com/forumdisplay.php?fid=63</a>"}]}